text: Baydavletovo () is a rural locality (a selo) in Baydavletovsky Selsoviet, Zianchurinsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 207 as of 2010. There is 1 street. == Geography == It is located 34 km from Isyangulovo, 6 km from Seregulovo. == References == Category:Rural localities in Zianchurinsky District
title: Baydavletovo
